					<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p>Back to the <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://share.coursera.org/wiki/index.php/Climateliteracy:Main">Climate Literacy Main Wiki Page</a></p>
<p>This page is meant to be a place to collect information about open access journals or journal articles about climate science and policy. Feel free to add! (NOTE: This is <strong>not</strong> a place for links to blog posts, though you're welcome to start another page for that.  Ideally, this list will focus on peer-reviewed literature)</p>
<p><strong>LIST OF OPEN-ACCESS JOURNALS</strong></p>
<p>To start, here's a link to the "Earth &amp; Environmental Sciences" page of the Directory of Open Access Journals. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.doaj.org/doaj?func=subject&amp;cpId=78&amp;uiLanguage=en">DOAJ</a></p>
<ul>
<li><p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.scirp.org/journal/ajcc/">American Journal of Climate Change</a></p></li>
<li><p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.revistas.unal.edu.co/index.php/rbct">Boletín de Ciencias de la Tierra</a></p></li>
<li><p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.sciencedomain.org/journal-home.php?id=10">British Journal of Environment and Climate Change</a></p></li>
<li><p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.earthscienceindia.info/">Earth Science India</a></p></li>
<li><p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.revistas.unal.edu.co/index.php/esrj/index">Earth Sciences Research Journal</a></p></li>
<li><p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.geologica-acta.com/HomeAC.do">Geologica Acta: an International Earth Science Journal</a></p></li>
<li><p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.omicsonline.org/jescchome.php">Journal of Earth Science &amp; Climatic Change</a></p></li>
<li><p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.scialert.net/jindex.php?issn=1994-7887">Journal of Environmental Science and Technology</a></p></li>
<li><p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://maxwellsci.com/jp/j2p.php?jid=RJEES">Research Journal of Environmental and Earth Sciences</a></p></li>
<li><p><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://webs.ono.com/reclim/">Revista de Climatología</a></p></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>LIST OF SPECIFIC OPEN-ACCESS ARTICLES THAT MAY BE OF INTEREST</strong></p>
<p><i>Please list alphabetically by the last name of the first author</i></p>
<ul>
<li><p>Cook, John, Dana Nuccitelli, Sarah A. Green, Mark Richardson, Bärbel Winkler, Rob Painting, Robert Way, Peter Jacobs, and Andrew Skuce, 2013. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://iopscience.iop.org/1748-9326/8/2/024024/article">Quantifying the consensus on anthropogenic global warming in the scientific literature</a>, Environmental Research Letters, vol 8, no 2. doi: 10.1088/1748-9326/8/2/024024
<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://iopscience.iop.org/1748-9326/8/2/024024/pdf/1748-9326_8_2_024024.pdf">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Foster, G., and S. Rahmstorf, 2011. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://iopscience.iop.org/1748-9326/6/4/044022/fulltext/">Global temperature evolution 1979–2010</a>, Environmental Research Letters, vol 6, 044022. doi: 10.1088/1748-9326/6/4/044022 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://iopscience.iop.org/1748-9326/6/4/044022/pdf/1748-9326_6_4_044022.pdf">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Griggs, J. A., J. E. Harries, 2007. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://journals.ametsoc.org/doi/abs/10.1175/JCLI4204.1">Comparison of Spectrally Resolved Outgoing Longwave Radiation over the Tropical Pacific between 1970 and 2003 Using IRIS, IMG, and AIRS</a>. Journal of Climate, 20, 3982-4001. doi: 10.1175/JCLI4204.1 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://web.gps.caltech.edu/~mlau/Griggs-07-IRIS-IMG-AIRS.pdf">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Hansen James E., and Makiko Sato, January 2012. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.fractual.co.za/Documents/Paleoclimate_Implications.pdf">Paleoclimate Implications for Human-Made Climate Change</a>. NASA Goddard Institute for Space Studies and Columbia University Earth Institute, New York.</p></li>
<li><p>Hansen, James E., Makiko Sato, Gary Russell, and Pushker Kharecha, September 2013. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://rsta.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/371/2001/20120294.full.html">Climate sensitivity, sea level and atmospheric carbon dioxide</a>. Phil. Trans. R. Soc. A, vol 371, 20120294, published 16 September 2013. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://rsta.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/371/2001/20120294.full.pdf+html">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Hansen, James, Makiko Sato, Reto Ruedy, Ken Lo, David W. Lea, and Martin Medina-Elizade, 2006. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.pnas.org/content/103/39/14288.full?sid=c4935483-9197-4644-9f3f-830b1c8b6520">Global temperature change</a>, Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences, vol 103, no 39, 14288-14293. doi: 10.1073/pnas.0606291103 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.pnas.org/content/103/39/14288.full.pdf+html">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Harries, John E., Helen E. Brindley, Peter J. Sagoo, and Richard J. Bantges, 2001. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.nature.com/nature/journal/v410/n6826/abs/410355a0.html">Increases in greenhouse forcing inferred from the outgoing longwave radiation spectra of the Earth in 1970 and 1997</a>, Nature 410, 355-357. doi: 10.1038/410355A0 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://workspace.imperial.ac.uk/physics/Public/spat/John/Increase%20in%20greenhouse%20forcing%20inferred%20from%20the%20outgoing%20longwave%20radiation%20spectra%20of%20the%20Earth%20in%201970%20and%201997.pdf">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Heide-Jørgensen, M.P., Kristin L. Laidre, Lori T. Quakenbush, and John J. Cittaet, 2012. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://rsbl.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/8/2/270">The Northwest Passage opens for bowhead whales</a>, Biology Letters, vol 8, no 2, 270-273. doi: 10.1098/rsbl.2011.0731 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://rsbl.royalsocietypublishing.org/content/8/2/270.full.pdf+html">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Hussein, Zekarias, Thomas Hertel, and Alla Golub, 2013. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://iopscience.iop.org/1748-9326/8/3/035009">Climate change mitigation policies and poverty in developing countries</a>, Environmental Research Letters, vol 8. doi:10.1088/1748-9326/8/3/035009 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://iopscience.iop.org/1748-9326/8/3/035009/pdf/1748-9326_8_3_035009.pdf">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>International Energy Agency, 2013. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldenergyoutlook.org/energyclimatemap/">Redrawing the Energy-Climate Map</a>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.worldenergyoutlook.org/media/weowebsite/2013/energyclimatemap/RedrawingEnergyClimateMap.pdf">PDF</a> </p></li>
<li><p>Kharecha, Pushker A., and James E. Hansen, 2013. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://pubs.acs.org/doi/full/10.1021/es3051197">Prevented Mortality and Greenhouse Gas Emissions from Historical and Projected Nuclear Power</a>, Environ. Sci. Technol., vol. 47, no. 9, 4889–4895. doi: 10.1021/es3051197 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://pubs.acs.org/doi/pdf/10.1021/es3051197">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Kouketsu, Shinya et al, 2011. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1029/2010JC006464/abstract">Deep ocean heat content changes estimated from observation and reanalysis product and their influence on sea level change</a>, Journal of Geophysical Research: Oceans, vol. 116 iss. C3. doi: 10.1029/2010JC006464 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="ftp://soest.hawaii.edu/coastal/Climate%20Articles/Ocean%20warming%20DEEP%20Kouketsu%202011.pdf">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Levitus, S., J.I. Antonov, T.P. Boyer, O.K. Baranova, H.E. Garcia, R.A. Locarnini, A.V. Mishonov, J.R. Reagan, D. Seidov, E.S. Yarosh, and M.M. Zweng, 2012. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1029/2012GL051106/abstract">World ocean heat content and thermosteric sea level change (0–2000 m), 1955–2010</a>. Geophysical Research Letters, vol. 39, iss. 10, L10603. doi:10.1029/2012GL051106 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="ftp://kakapo.ucsd.edu/pub/sio_220/e03%20-%20Global%20warming/Levitus_et_al.GRL12.pdf">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Lobell, David B., and Sharon M. Gourdji, 2012. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.plantphysiol.org/content/160/4/1686.full">The Influence of Climate Change on Global Crop Productivity</a>, Plant Physiology, vol. 160 no. 4 1686-1697 doi: ​10.​1104/​pp.​112.​208298 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.plantphysiol.org/content/160/4/1686.full.pdf+html">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Murphy, D. M., S. Solomon, R. W. Portmann, K. H. Rosenlof, P. M. Forster, and T. Wong, 2009. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1029/2009JD012105/abstract">An observationally based energy balance for the Earth since 1950</a>, Journal of Geophysical Research, vol. 114 iss. D17. doi: 10.1029/2009JD012105 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.iup.uni-heidelberg.de/institut/studium/lehre/Uphysik/PhysicsClimate/2009JD012105.pdf">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Shepherd, Andrew et al, 2012. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.sciencemag.org/content/338/6111/1183">A Reconciled Estimate of Ice-Sheet Mass Balance</a>, Science, vol. 338 no. 6111 1183-1189 doi: 10.1126/science.1228102 <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.staff.science.uu.nl/~lenae101/pubs/Shepherd2012.pdf">PDF</a></p></li>
<li><p>Thackeray, Stephen J. et al, 2010. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1365-2486.2010.02165.x/full">Trophic level asynchrony in rates of phenological change for marine, freshwater and terrestrial environments</a>, Global Change Biology, vol. 16 iss. 12 3304-3313 doi: 10.1111/j.1365-2486.2010.02165.x <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1365-2486.2010.02165.x/pdf">PDF</a></p></li>
</ul>

